'''The Lord of the Rings MUSH''' is a cancelled video game. It was to be the succesor of a [[The Lord of the Rings MUSH (1993 video game)|game with the same name]]. In story and design it was similar to the original, but the coding was significantly improved in comparison with the other game.It was cancelled for unknown reasons.
